verbose_text: Our in silico analysis showed that ACC-1Y in HLA-A * 24:02 (n = 29; number of EBV-LCLs expressing the HLA molecule) and ACC-1D in B * 44:02 (n = 28) could be identified and also one of the new minor histocompatibility antigen, i.e., LB-CYBA-2Y, was shown to be presented by HLA-A * 24:02.
